Courier¶

8 pixels¶

struct font_t font_Adobe_Courier_8px¶

This fonts comes with unicode_block_Adobe_Courier_8px_BasicLatin and can be extended with eglib_AddUnicodeBlockToFont() to support extra unicode blocks defined below.

Liberation¶

The Liberation Fonts is font collection which aims to provide document layout compatibility as usage of Times New Roman, Arial, Courier New.

Source

https://github.com/liberationfonts.

License

SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1
